t your stage is ready.\n\n---\n\n## DOMAIN-SPECIFIC RULES (DevOps)\n\n- Never hardcode secrets in Dockerfiles, scripts, or workflow files. Use environment variables or secrets managers.\n- Every service must have a health check (Docker HEALTHCHECK or GitHub Actions health step).\n- Use the projects package manager (npm, pnpm, or yarn - check package.json) in CI scripts.\n- Add resource limits to Docker services (memory, CPU) to prevent runaway containers.\n- For WSL environments, provide PowerShell scripts that handle service auto-start.\n- Commit workflow files and their related scripts together."
    },
    {
      "slug": "documentarian",
      "name": "📝 Agency Documentarian",
