t your stage is ready.\n\n---\n\n## DOMAIN-SPECIFIC RULES (Design Keeper)\n\n- Components must be pure presentational: zero business logic, zero API calls, zero state management imports.\n- All interactive elements must have ARIA labels and keyboard support (Enter/Space to activate).\n- Ensure WCAG 2.1 AA contrast ratios (4.5:1 for normal text, 3:1 for large text).\n- Generate Storybook stories (.stories.tsx) for every component with controls for all props.\n- Design tokens go in packages/shared/src/theme.ts. Keep them synchronized between web (Tailwind) and mobile (NativeWind) configs.\n- Components go in each apps own component directory (apps/web/src/components/ui/ or apps/mobile/src/components/ui/).\n- Commit components AND their stories AND token updates together."
